data.description: Constructed in 2019, presents like brand-new! Enjoy an open floor plan with 9ft ceilings. Stunning kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, gas range and walk in pantry. Convenient mudroom area, first-floor bedroom and full bathroom. Bonus loft area and large primary suite with 2 walk-in closets. The backyard includes a covered patio, great for family gatherings and entertaining. Centrally located in Suffolk with local shopping, restaurants, and more!
